data.description: Beautifully Remodeled Island Home! A dramatic foyer welcomes you into the spacious floorplan, with abundant windows for plenty of natural light! A large living area provides easy access to the roomy kitchen, with built-in appliances and tons of cabinet storage. The downstairs bonus room is the perfect space for an office or second living area, while the separate dining room provides the perfect setting for holiday feasts! The split-bedroom floorplan affords privacy to the downstairs Master Suite, while two upstairs bedrooms ensures room for all. Enjoy warm afternoons from your luxurious in-ground pool, or escape the sun and relax under the covered patio, with xeriscaping for easy maintenance and privacy fencing for quiet enjoyment! Located just moments from the community boat ramp and just a short drive from the beaches North Padre is famous for! Enjoy Island Living today!
